entries.journal_entry_description: The Civilian Protection guild representative on Kashyyyk wants to speak with you about recent encounters with the Ghrag mercenary clan.
entries.journal_entry_title: Contact Eyma of the Civilian Protection guild
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You will find the venerable nautolan named 'Eyma' located near the Kachirho starport. Tell him everything you know about the Ghrag mercenary clan.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Talk to Eyma of the Civilian Protection Guild
